The infrastructure continues building on itself. Database endpoints are ready for application integration. CloudFront origins are configured for the ALB from Lab 3. Route 53 health checks are monitoring the entire stack. WAF rules are protecting at the edge. Each lab creates integration points for what comes next.


Labs 7-8 (ELB & Lambda/API Gateway) are currently in progress, rolling out over the coming days.


